	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "His place in the list in the SC de agro Pergameno suggests that he was then of praetorian rank (129 B.C.); see Wiseman, NM 210, no. 15; Sherk, RDGE no. 12, pp. 63-73. On the date, see below on M'. Aquillius (10).\n" .
